  author    = {Aramaki, T. and Boezio, M. and Boggs, S. E. and Bonvicini, V. and Bridges, G. and Campana, D. and Craig, W. W. and von Doetinchem, P. and Everson, E. and Fabris, L. and Feldman, S. and Fuke, H. and Gahbauer, F. and Gerrity, C. and Ghislotti, L. and Hailey, C. J. and Hayashi, T. and Kawachi, A. and Kozai, M. and Lazzaroni, P. and Law, M. and Lenni, A. and Lowell, A. and Manghisoni, M. and Marcelli, N. and Mizukoshi, K. and Mocchiutti, E. and Mochizuki, B. and Mognet, S. A. I. and Munakata, K. and Munini, R. and Okazaki, S. and Olson, J. and Ong, R. A. and Osteria, G. and Perez, K. and Perfetto, F. and Quinn, S. and Re, V. and Riceputi, E. and Roach, B. and Rogers, F. and Ryan, J. L. and Saffold, N. and Scotti, V. and Shimizu, Y. and Shutt, K. and Sparvoli, R. and Stoessl, A. and Tiberio, A. and Vannuccini, E. and Xiao, M. and Yamatani, M. and Yee, K. and Yoshida, T. and Zampa, G. and Zeng, J. and Zweerink, J.},
